---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About — TylahJadeArt">
  <nav class="fixed top-0 left-0 right-0 z-50 px-8 py-6 flex justify-between items-center bg-jaded-bg/80 backdrop-blur-md border-b border-white/5">
    <a href="/" class="flex items-center gap-3">
      <img src="/favicon.svg" alt="Dragon" class="w-10 h-10" />
      <span class="text-xl font-display font-bold tracking-tight">
        <span class="text-dusty-pink">JADED</span>
        <span class="text-muted-sage"> × </span>
        <span class="text-cream">TylahJade</span>
      </span>
    </a>
    <div class="flex gap-8 text-sm text-muted-silver">
      <a href="/design" class="hover:text-moss-green transition-colors">Design</a>
      <a href="/art" class="text-moss-green">Art</a>
    </div>
  </nav>

  <main>
    <section class="min-h-[70vh] flex items-center px-6 pt-32 pb-20 relative overflow-hidden">
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-art-bg via-charcoal to-art-surface/50"></div>
      <div class="absolute w-80 h-80 bg-moss-green/5 rounded-full blur-3xl top-20 right-20"></div>

      <div class="max-w-4xl relative z-10">
        <p class="text-moss-green text-xs tracking-[0.3em] uppercase mb-6">The Artistic Hemisphere</p>
        <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-display font-bold mb-8 leading-tight">
          <span class="text-cream">Made with</span>
          <span class="text-moss-green"> heart.</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="text-muted-silver text-xl max-w-2xl leading-relaxed">
          TylahJadeArt is the tactile, emotional side of the creative mind — where ideas take physical form through paint, clay, texture, and hands-on making.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-24 px-6 border-t border-white/5">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <h2 class="text-xs tracking-[0.3em] text-cream/40 uppercase mb-12">The Approach</h2>
        <div class="space-y-16">
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-display text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-moss-green">Emotion Over Perfection</h3>
            <p class="text-muted-silver leading-relaxed text-lg">
              The best work comes from feeling, not from technique. I lean into imperfection — the drip that wasn't planned, the texture that appeared by accident. Those moments make a piece feel alive.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-display text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-moss-green">Texture Tells Stories</h3>
            <p class="text-muted-silver leading-relaxed text-lg">
              Every layer in a painting is a decision. Scraping back reveals history. Building up creates depth. The surface of a piece should be a landscape you want to touch.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-display text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-moss-green">Two Worlds, One Voice</h3>
            <p class="text-muted-silver leading-relaxed text-lg">
              The digital precision of JADED DESIGN and the raw expressiveness of TylahJadeArt aren't contradictions — they're complements. The strategic thinking feeds the intuitive making, and vice versa.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-24 px-6 bg-art-surface/30">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <h2 class="text-xs tracking-[0.3em] text-cream/40 uppercase mb-12">The Artist Behind TylahJade</h2>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-start">
          <div>
            <div class="aspect-square bg-gradient-to-br from-dusty-pink/20 to-moss-green/20 rounded-3xl flex items-center justify-center">
              <span class="text-6xl opacity-20">👤</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-display text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Tylah</h3>
            <p class="text-muted-silver leading-relaxed mb-6">
              A multidisciplinary artist and designer working across physical and digital mediums. Making things that feel — paintings that grab you, ceramics that invite touch, spaces that shift how you feel when you're in them.
            </p>
            <p class="text-muted-silver leading-relaxed">
              The work is personal. Some pieces are memories made visible. Others are questions that haven't been answered yet. All of it is an attempt to understand what it means to be a creative being in a beautiful, chaotic world.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-24 px-6 text-center border-t border-white/5">
      <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-display font-bold mb-6 text-cream">Commissions & Collaborations</h2>
        <p class="text-muted-silver mb-10">Interested in a custom painting, mural, or collaborative project? Let's talk.</p>
        <a href="/art/work-with-us" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-8 py-4 bg-gradient-to-r from-moss-green to-dusty-pink text-charcoal font-medium rounded-full hover:opacity-90 transition-all">
          Get in touch
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>

    <footer class="py-12 px-6 border-t border-white/5">
      <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-center gap-6">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
          <img src="/favicon.svg" alt="Dragon" class="w-6 h-6" />
          <span class="text-sm text-muted-silver">
            <span class="text-dusty-pink">JADED</span>
            <span class="text-muted-sage"> × </span>
            <span class="text-cream">TylahJade</span>
          </span>
        </div>
        <p class="text-muted-silver text-xs">© 2025 TylahJadeArt. All rights reserved.</p>
        <div class="flex gap-6 text-xs text-muted-silver">
          <a href="/art" class="hover:text-moss-green transition-colors">Gallery</a>
          <a href="/art/about" class="hover:text-moss-green transition-colors">About</a>
          <a href="/art/work-with-us" class="hover:text-moss-green transition-colors">Inquire</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </footer>
  </main>
</Layout>